name: River Ripple Earrings
description:
A transparent agate round is set on waved silver to mimic a stream. The piece is clever simplicity with the agate placed midform.

	The Agate is 5mm and the earring hangs 1.8in/4.6cm with the 1.25in/3.1cm dangle.

name: Pearl and Moonstone Bookmark
description:
This lovely silvertone bookmark makes the perfect treat for someone who enjoys a good story. The bookhook is adorned with fine silver links carrying pearls and moonstone. The hook piece is 4.75 inches long while the link is about 1.8 inches. Each is made to ensure secure page holding:)

	Full Moon ~ Coin Pearl, Moonstone & Freshwater Pearls (White/ Iridescent)

name: Swivel Pearl Earrings
description:
These simple earwires were designed to add a twist to basic earring. A soft mauve pearl hangs center with an offshoot of half looped silver.

	The Pearl is 7mm and the earwire hangs 1 in/2.5cm with the .5in/1.3cm extension
Sterling Silver/ Dyed Freshwater Pearl
